## Definition Of A Good Telemetry Outcome

A good Lens change should usually improve at least one of these:

- fewer bridge connections per task
- fewer setup cycles
- fewer `get_tool_schema` calls
- fewer pack transitions
- smaller shaped payloads
- fewer unmatched requests outside expected reload/play transitions
- full TSAM stage coverage for split tools
- clearer failure classes and recovery hints
